General Assembly Raised Bill No. 5281
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 465
Referred to Committee on PLANNING AND
DEVELOPMENT
Introduced by:
(PD)
AN ACT CONCERNING PLANNING AND DEVELOPMENT.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 Section 1. Section 8-28 of the general statutes is repealed and the
2 following is substituted in lieu thereof (Effective October 1, 2026):
3 Notice of all official actions or decisions of a planning commission,
4 not limited to those relating to the approval or denial of subdivision
5 plans, shall be published in a newspaper having a substantial circulation
6 in the municipality [within] not later than fifteen days after such action
7 or decision. Any appeal from an action or decision of a planning
8 commission shall be taken pursuant to the provisions of section 8-8.
This act shall take effect as follows and shall amend the following
sections:
Section 1 October 1, 2026 8-28
PD Joint Favorable
